If you have placed this widget in the Page Profile Placement area and you "lock" it, then Page Owners will NOT be able to remove it or drag-n-drop it.
Visit your Insights Circle: If you have NOT placed this widget in the Page Profile Placement area and you "lock" it, then this widget will NOT be available to Page Owners for placing on the Page. If you have placed this widget in the Page Profile Placement area and you "lock" it, then Circle Owners will NOT be able to remove it or drag-n-drop it.

From the Global Settings of this plugin, you have allowed Page Owners to be able to arrange, add and remove widgets from the profile of their Pages. However, you still have control over what Page Profile widgets should be available to Page Owners, which widgets they should NOT be able to remove, and which ones they should be able to remove. If you have added a new plugin on your site, and would like its widget to be shown on Page Profiles and NOT be removable by Page Owners, then you can drop that widget into Page Profile below. If you would like to show an announcement, or any HTML content on Page Profiles, and NOT allow Page Owners to be able to remove it, then you can do that as well below. If there is a widget coming on profiles of Pages of your site that you want to be removed, then you can do that below; and many more such actions. If you drop a widget from a different plugin into the Page Profile, then Page Owners will NOT be able to remove it or drag-n-drop it. If you "lock" a Page Profile widget that has NOT been placed in the Page Profile Placement area, then that widget will NOT be available to Page Owners for placing on the Page. If you "lock" a Page Profile widget that has been placed in the Page Profile Placement area, then Page Owners will NOT be able to remove it or drag-n-drop it.
NOTE: If you have placed "Ad Campaign" or "Html Block" on this page, then once you click on the "Save Changes" link, you will neither be able to change the position nor edit that block. So, if you want to do so, you will have to remove that block from the Page and save changes and then place it again from the Available Blocks.

Visit your Insights Page: Displays the insights of your Page to your Page Admins only. These insights include metrics like views, likes, comments and active users of the Page.
Visit your Insights Circle: Displays the insights of your Page to your Page Admins only. These insights include metrics like views, likes, comments and active users of the Circle.

Visit your Insights Page: Displays the Apps related links for your Page. This widget should be placed in the left column.
Visit your Insights Circle: Displays the Apps related links for your Circle. This widget should be placed in the left column.

Visit your Insights Page: Displays Linked Pages of your Page.
Visit your Insights Circle: Displays Linked Pages of your Circle.

Visit your Insights Page: Displays the Featured Admins of your Page.
Visit your Insights Circle: Displays the Featured Admins of your Circle.

Visit your Insights Page: Displays the thumb photo of a Page. This works as an alternate profile photo when you have set the layout of Page Profile to be tabbed, from the Page Layout Settings, and have integrated with the "Advertisements / Community Ads Plugin" by SocialEngineAddOns. In that case, the left column of the Page Profile having the main profile photo gets hidden to accomodate Ads. This widget must be placed on the Page Profile at the top of middle column.
Visit your Insights Circle: Displays the thumb photo of a Page. This works as an alternate profile photo when you have set the layout of Page Profile to be tabbed, from the Page Layout Settings, and have integrated with the "Advertisements / Community Ads Plugin" by SocialEngineAddOns. In that case, the left column of the Page Profile having the main profile photo gets hidden to accomodate Ads. This widget must be placed on the Circle Profile at the top of middle column.

Visit your Insights Circle: Displays the thumb photo of your Page. This widget must be placed on the Circle Profile at the top of middle column. This photo shows up only in special cases.

Visit your Insights Page: This widget contains the Facebook Like Box which enables Page Admins to gain Likes for their Facebook Page from this website. The edit popup contains the settings to customize the Facebook Like Box. This widget should be placed on the Page Profile.
Visit your Insights Circle: This widget contains the Facebook Like Box which enables Page Admins to gain Likes for their Facebook Page from this website. The edit popup contains the settings to customize the Facebook Like Box. This widget should be placed on the Circle Profile.
